{"tid":1605732,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（政事）10月1日 13:00 銅鑼灣東角道集合 遊行去中環","createTime":"2019-09-30T11:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T04:29:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7d4fe9d366c3d1cbb6962846a2155cd50b3627","tid":1605732,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:20:43.000Z","msg":"（政事）10月1日<br />\n13:00<br />\n銅鑼灣東角道集合<br />\n遊行去中環<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒有國慶 祇有國殤<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n結束專政 還政於民<br />\n_______________________<br />\n<br />\n李卓人會見傳媒，宣布承接明天民陣原本遊行路缐，下午一時銅鑼灣東角道集合，遊行到中環遮打道行人專用區。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2480254742062289/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F2480254742062289%2F&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZgKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=34e53617\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2480254742062289/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Op5cYY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Op5cYY.png&h=d39bf5ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7a4104b9de6f8090d4fb502742696c1954360bb","tid":1605732,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:24:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>聽日我會去遊行</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n黑色衫就係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我"},{"pid":"8e2557a8cfd67fb8efcb38517feb3d02cd6ce178","tid":1605732,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:30:15.000Z","msg":"俊仁bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3b1b1c64cfd3efe6691bbc3e66e7e04cc68943","tid":1605732,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7a4104b9de6f8090d4fb502742696c1954360bb","tid":1605732,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:24:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color